How to install:


Move the the content to a folder named "beacon" in the modules folder.

Create an account at http://www.beaconpush.com if you don't already 
have one and find your API key and Secret key (go to your account page).

Apply you API key and Secret key inside the module config file (the 
only file inside the configs folder)

Enable the module in your bootstrap.php file.

Have fun with real-time features!